Setting of Karabiner(Keyremap4macbook)
Mainly for external keyboard:Filco Ninja
From win-layout to mac-layout
One setting for internal keyboard

HOWTO:
  Install Karabiner (https://pqrs.org/osx/karabiner/)
  cp ~/dotfiles/Karabiner/private.xml ~/Library/Application\ Support/Karabiner
  press buttom ReloadXML on Karabiner preference
  toggle:
    "My Private Setting For Filco"
    "My Private Setting For Internal Keyboard"
    "Control_L to Control_L(+When you type Control_L only send Escape)"

Misc:
  remember to modify key Repeat
    Delay Until Repeat 100ms
    Key Repeat          10ms
  Cap-> Ctrl-L:
    In System Preference->Keyboard->Modifier Keys, change "Caps" to "Ctrl" for both keyboards

Main settings:
  For Filco Ninja Keyboard
    map application key to fn key
    switch option keys and command keys
    function keys for special features
    fn + function key for original function keys(F1, F2, etc)
  For Internal Keyboard
    option right to control right

Reference:
  Karabiner (https://pqrs.org/osx/karabiner/)
  KeyCode https://github.com/tekezo/KeyRemap4MacBook/blob/version_8.0.0/src/bridge/generator/keycode/data/KeyCode.data
  ConsumerKeyCode https://github.com/tekezo/KeyRemap4MacBook/blob/version_8.0.0/src/bridge/generator/keycode/data/ConsumerKeyCode.data
